data.description: Welcome to a beautiful property that offers an elegant charm and modern convenience. This home's fireplace undoubtedly gives it a cozy and homely feel, perfect for those cold winter nights. Its neutral color paint scheme invites a serene ambiance and is freshly done over the interiors, offering an almost look of newness to the home. The primary bathroom has been lovingly crafted to include a separate tub and shower to maximize comfort. The gourmet kitchen comes with all stainless steel appliances and boasts a spacious that offers  for all culinary needs. For flooring, partial replacements have been made, demonstrating our commitment to maintaining the home's high standards. The highlight is the outdoor patio space that facilitates tranquil relaxation or casual entertaining, perfect for any season. The backyard, completely fenced in, offers privacy while creating the perfect outdoor retreat. Indeed, this property provides a unique blend of character, quality, and convenience, making it a dream home that one could truly enjoy living in.
